Package: ANECO
Type: Package
Title: Tools for the analysis of ecoacoustic indices
Version: 0.1.0
Author: TELESIG, ICOMVIS, Universidad Nacional de Costa Rica
Maintainer: Jimmy Barrantes Madrigal <jimmybarrantesm@gmail.com>
Description: ANECO is an R package for ecoacoustic analysis that streamlines the calculation of nearly 30 acoustic indices, including underexplored metrics. It offers tools for sound pressure calibration and automated detection of rain and cicada-dominated recordings. Designed for ease of use, ANECO supports efficient workflows and encourages multi-index approaches for robust ecological interpretation.
